# Add Shapes, Image Upload, and Undo/Redo to Canvas

This plan outlines the steps to introduce new shape nodes (Circle, Rectangle, Arrow), image upload capability, and functional Undo/Redo actions to the roadmap canvas.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]  
> Please review the approach for the **Image Upload**. Instead of storing large images directly inside the canvas JSON (which can slow things down), I will create a small endpoint in the backend to save the image file and return a URL. The canvas will store this URL. Does this approach work for you?

## Open Questions

> [!WARNING]  
> Are Arrow and Line intended to be floating nodes that you drag and drop, or do you want them to be tools that draw connection lines between existing nodes? For this plan, I'll implement them as standard draggable nodes so you can freely place and resize arrows on the canvas, similar to Miro or FigJam.

